inlineContent.text: Uniform type identifiers declare common types for resources an app loads, saves, or opens from other apps. Apps that use proprietary types can define them by using the systemâ€™s unified type identifiers as base types.

abstract.text: Provide uniform type identifiers that describe file types for storage or transfer.
